|Comments=As of now, we have two schemas and schema families for bureaucracy, one for the Western loanword and the other its Persian neologism. Both terms are used interchangeably and extensively in Persian-language blogs, the Persian neologism is favored  more in official writings. We have not concluded yet any reasons to warrant the existence of two schemas for the same concept. All the same both schemas are inter-connected and appear under the schema families as well. We need to discuss this in our upcoming meeting. 

