{{Schema
|Name gloss=Lifting an_object
|Comments=Although the current Persian schema has been linked to the English schema "Moving object" the Persian schema does not seem to be appropriate for it
 Under consideration of the related lemmas referring to action verbs such as "destroy, annihilate, eradicate, extirpate", the verb should be changed into the compound verb "از میان برداشتن " which more closely approximates the Persian lemmas. Therefore, the Persian schema should be linked to another English schema.
|Tags=Program sources
|Type=Frame
|Status=in development, auto imported
|Last reviewed by=Reza
|Roles=
|Related schemas={{Related schema
|Related schema.Relation type=is subcase of
|Related schema.Name=جسم
}}
|Bindings=
|Inferences=
|Relevant LUs={{LUs
|LUs.Language=Persian
|LUs.Lemmas=رفع
}}{{LUs
|LUs.Language=Persian
|LUs.Lemmas=زدودن
}}{{LUs
|LUs.Language=Persian
|LUs.Lemmas=از میان بردن
}}{{LUs
|LUs.Language=Persian
|LUs.Lemmas=از بین بردن
}}
