{{Schema |Name gloss=Providing educational possibilities |Comments=This schema does not fully correspond with the English schema Educational opportunities
Not sure whether the long Persian schema should be deleted i.e. placed under # 3(see the document shared on the Google drive "Schemas & Metaphors with missing fields"(i.e. Persian schema has not been defined adequately ) or at least- due to the length of the schema- should be renamed by changing the first part,the verbal element, of the schema to a noun such as mohayya saazi In most cases where the Persian schema -especially by using combined verbal elements are too long, those parts can be substituted by a non verbal synonym
